quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  83,7,"No indeed! Verily the deeds of the wicked are in the Record locked up in the prison-house!"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  83,8,"And how would you know what the Record of the prison-house is?"
  83,9,"It is a Book inscribed."
  83,10,"Woe, then, to those that give the lie,"